  "description": "A broad-shouldered woman of middle years, marked by the compact musculature and steady posture common to long service behind a public bar. Brown eyes sit under straight brows and remain notably unblinking, while brown hair is kept in a practical ponytail that leaves the face clear. Bronze skin shows a fine network of old heat-marks along the forearms consistent with repeated contact with scalding vessels. The voice is controlled and even, suited to the measured cadence of a working bartender.",
